   "source": [
    "# M25CSA028 — ResNet-18 Evaluation on GPU\n",
    "This notebook:\n",
    "1. Clones your GitHub repo\n",
    "2. Uploads `setA.pth` and the `data/` folder from Google Drive\n",
    "3. Runs full evaluation (overall accuracy, per-class accuracy, classification report)\n",
    "4. Plots and saves confusion matrix\n",
    "5. Runs single-image inference on `data/test/5/340.png`\n",
    "6. Commits results back to GitHub"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
